data.description:
Discover the perfect 3-bed/2-bath/2-car garage oasis in the coveted gated community of Lake Charles. This immaculate home boasts tranquil preserve views and a host of desirable amenities.The heart of this home is the sunlit kitchen, complete with a beautiful dining space in front of the large picture window to truly appreciate the serene backyard views.The master suite is a private sanctuary with double doors, an ensuite bathroom, and ample closet space. Two additional guest bedrooms offer flexibility for guests or additional living spaces.This home boasts newer appliances as well as a newer AC system, ensuring worry-free living.Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the screened and covered patio, as well as the open paver patio, offering multiple entertaining spaces. Lake Charles boasts one of the lowest HOA fees in Saint Lucie West, making this community even more appealing. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shops, dining, hospitals, interstates, golf, baseball, beaches, and all that Florida living has to offer.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this outstanding property your forever home!
